{"tid":367512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係睇唔起個垃圾啊哥","createTime":"2017-08-20T19:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T17:22:58.000Z","uid":106847,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84db848dbe1fa47d0ed0f5adf4d5454a0b36c07f","tid":367512,"uid":106847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:13:02.000Z","msg":"我啊哥廿幾歲人 工又唔諗住搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正係識訓同打機, 做下家務就以為自己好盡責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就等老母比錢<br />\n又唔話得 又唔肯改變下自己<br />\n比人話兩句 問兩句就起晒鋼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一啲上進心都無 真係好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問有個咁廢嘅呀哥,可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145a16bdc1ba92eac2ab37821fda1fc0de2004e8","tid":367512,"uid":27396,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:15:51.000Z","msg":"幫媽媽減少負擔 幫手比零用錢啊哥"},{"pid":"191405dd7944b655dfdb9b3e300e064dc2d8fd6f","tid":367512,"uid":106847,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫媽媽減少負擔 幫手比零用錢啊哥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點比得落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢仲廢過我樓下啲廢老"},{"pid":"2816dd4d0d6b8e49fa22ea2ccba80a3f9e5f0007","tid":367512,"uid":72045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:19:02.000Z","msg":"阿媽仲會俾錢咁神奇？<br />\n我阿哥好少少，就係會返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係當正自己大爺咁款"},{"pid":"dd17d8725bf13bea7be3a455c88a482612cff16c","tid":367512,"uid":72454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:21:03.000Z","msg":"我阿哥又係廢青<br />\n話兩句就發爛炸<br />\n真係想屌能死佢"},{"pid":"297d8029afb65faba2b2d322e2f2a9c2cb16c951","tid":367512,"uid":106847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-2