rmal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9520761dd8c0dc7e7618df16f86fca5b471f6f50","tid":367512,"uid":106847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀完書幾多年？<br />\n有無咩特別原因唔返工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原因就係唔肯面對要搵工呢個事實 <br />\n想繼續hea<br />\n佢係今年先讀完書 但佢都係無讀過啲咩出黎係對佢有幫助,<br />\n然後逃避"},{"pid":"9bb7afc6af8692c6dc9e8b04b4f0700a53781949","tid":367512,"uid":106847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>阿媽仲會俾錢咁神奇？<br />\n我阿哥好少少，就係會返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係當正自己大爺咁款</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老母都怕左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲呀哥係覺得自己長子就大晒嫁啦<br />\n好撚麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔單止對我係咁<br />\n對老豆老母都係咁<br />\n十問九唔應<br />\n要佢做野果陣就扮聽唔到<br />\n人地認真果陣佢就當人玩<br />\n搞到人發火就話人唔玩得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲人應該要趕佢出街受下苦先識長大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ba64fd5c96cc6283250bde74900a1cc6787957","tid":367512,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T06:20:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讀完書幾多年？<br />\n有無咩特別原因唔返工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原因就係唔肯面對要搵工呢個事實 <br />\n想繼續hea<br />\n佢係今年先讀完書 但佢都係無讀過啲咩出黎係對佢有幫助,<br />\n然後逃避</blockquote><br />\n都係今年啫俾d時間佢"},{"pid":"ace6e15eef13f717d7c541dac9fe9269bbc8a17f","tid":367512,"uid":1021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌，我啊哥廢左十幾年啦，淨係瞓覺打機，永遠唔出街，家務唔會做，成撚日發癲亂鬧人，屈人想害佢，但其實根本就無人想理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾多歲😱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三十頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24c59794eb156cff3dc52f3958a80ce227